# Data Linkage Table

The data linkage table lists all the different original data sets for your project, as all as metadata about each of them:

- What is the source of the data?
- What is the *unit of observation* for each data table?
- Which data tables can be linked to each other? Which column or combination of columns can be used to link them?
- How will you refer to each data table? Where are each of them stored? Where are they back up?

